        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Aye, there is one thing that weighs on us. My kinsman Gloisin had his family's heirloom — his coat of arms — stolen by a brigand named Gerrey Halliams, who fled south to the Ruins of Dale. None of us can be spared to chase him. Would you recover it?"
          }
